divs: Sighting DetailsWe were watching fireworks and noticed very bright object that looked almost fire like. Object made no sound. It seemed to pulsate some. We noticed it heading NW then head W. A plane was close by then object faded. This happened right about 9:50pm EST. Event lasted maybe 5 minutes from when we first noticed it.
